  - m_Id: 70754471448576
    m_Localized: Whetstone
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 72785835790336
    m_Localized: 'You inflict more damage when doing a parry.

      Leveling up
      will increase this damage bonus.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73066078212096
    m_Localized: 'You inflict more damage when doing a perfect parry.

      Leveling
      up will increase this damage bonus.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73202745413632
    m_Localized: 'You inflict more damage when you parried all the attacks of an
      enemy''s combo.

      Leveling up will increase this damage bonus.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73305019322368
    m_Localized: 'Slow down your enemy''s movement the more perfect parry in a row
      you have.

      Leveling up will increase the amount of slow down.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73491716182016
    m_Localized: 'Inflict damage each time you successfully perfect parry enough
      time in a row.

      Leveling up will decrease the number of perfect parry
      required to inflict damage.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73602215120896
    m_Localized: 'The damage you inflicted increases the more perfect parry in a
      row you do.

      Leveling up will increase your damage even more.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73716631539712
    m_Localized: 'Ignore a hit when the number of perfect parry in a row is big enough.
      It will reset the perfect parry in a row count.

      Leveling up will decrease
      the number of perfect parry to take effect.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 73935574208512
    m_Localized: 'The less life you have, the more damage you apply to the enemy.

      Leveling
      up increases the damage.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74068621725696
    m_Localized: 'When you do a perfect parry, you have a chance to lower the number
      of attacks in the current enemy combo.

      Leveling up increases the chance
      of this happening.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74177539411968
    m_Localized: 'You have a chance to ignore the first attack you fail to parry
      during a combo.

      Leveling up will increase that chance.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74275182809088
    m_Localized: 'Slow down your enemy''s wind down movement.

      Leveling up
      will increase the amount of slow down.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74410373615616
    m_Localized: 'When you do a non-perfect parry, you have a chance it counts as
      a perfect parry.

      Leveling up increases the chance of this happening.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74545258237952
    m_Localized: 'Increase your maximum life.

      Leveling up will increase your
      maximum life even more.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74675688509440
    m_Localized: 'You receive more damage but inflict more damage as well.

      Leveling
      up will increase the amount of damage, both for you and your enemy.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 74928219164672
    m_Localized: 'If you perfect parry every attack of a combo, you recover a bit
      of life.

      Leveling up will increase the amount of life recovered.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75068141146112
    m_Localized: 'Increase the time before the next combo after a perfect parry.

      Leveling
      up will increase the amount of delay.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75225045864448
    m_Localized: 'You have a small chance to ignore any attack you fail to parry.

      Leveling
      up will increase that chance.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75311679213568
    m_Localized: 'You have a chance that a perfect parry counts as two to calculate
      the number of perfect parries in a row you did.

      Leveling up increases
      the chance of this to happen.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75426640891904
    m_Localized: 'Once per fight, survive death and come back with a small life amount.

      Leveling
      up will increase the amount of life you come back with.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75570958503936
    m_Localized: 'When you fail to parry an attack, you have a chance to stop the
      enemy''s combo.

      Leveling up will increase that chance.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 75785400684544
    m_Localized: 'Parrying perfectly an attack will enhance all damage you inflict
      until the end of the combo.

      Leveling up will increase the amount of
      damage inflicted.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76008105644032
    m_Localized: 'When you do a perfect parry, there is an additional chance that
      the next attack comes from the top.

      Leveling up will increase this chance.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76103433785344
    m_Localized: 'Slow down your enemy''s wind up movement.

      Leveling up will
      increase the amount of slow down.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76229661364224
    m_Localized: 'After 3 perfect parry in a row, you inflict damage on your enemy.

      Leveling
      up will increase the amount of damage.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76346464342016
    m_Localized: 'The damage you received decrease the more perfect parry in a row
      you do.

      Leveling up will decrease the damage even more.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76474172510208
    m_Localized: 'Heal yourself between fights.

      Leveling up will increase
      the amount of life restored.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76622789283840
    m_Localized: 'Slow down the next enemy attack after a perfect parry.

      Leveling
      up will increase the amount of slow down.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 76730268323840
    m_Localized: 'Enhance every damage you inflict on your enemy by a small amount.

      Leveling
      up will increase the amount of damage inflicted.'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1090990238797824
    m_Localized: Select
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
